query:
SELECT
                u.address AS "address!",
                (
                    SELECT
                        nonce
                    FROM
                        account_properties
                    WHERE
                        address = u.address
                        AND miniblock_number <= $2
                    ORDER BY
                        miniblock_number DESC
                    LIMIT
                        1
                ) AS "nonce?"
            FROM
                UNNEST($1::bytea []) AS u (address)
